text: Bommanahalli is a locality in Bengaluru and one of the zones of BBMP.http://www.census2011.co.in/data/village/611611-bommanahalli- karnataka.html It is located adjacent to Hosur Road National Highway 7 in India and is proximate to the IT hub Electronics City. Two of The Oxford Educational Institutions are located in Bommanahalli, the Oxford College of Engineering and the Oxford Dental College, Hospital and Research Center. The joint commissioner of the zone is currently Rama Krishna. ==References== Category:Neighbourhoods in Bangalore
